	<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;" align="left">
		<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', 'serif';line-height:150%;">(</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;">七</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', 'serif';line-height:150%;">)</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;">采购业务</span> 
